244: To add a field override, follow these steps:
245: 
246: 1. Navigate to the panel to which you want to add the data link.
247: 1. Hover over any part of the panel to display the menu icon in the upper-right corner.
248: 1. Click the menu icon and select **Edit** to open the panel editor.
